		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">BASIC CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Highlight selection, change viewpoint, alter contact point, angle of strike on cue ball -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad</font>			  
                  <br>&nbsp; Confirm, begin shot -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Cancel -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle Button</font>				  
                  <br>&nbsp; Alter point that you will strike on cue ball -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square Button</font>	
                  <br>&nbsp; Alter angle to strike ball -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Triangle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Zoom in -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;L1 Button</font>	
                  <br>&nbsp; Zoom out -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;R1 Button</font>	
                  <br>&nbsp; Toggle ball numbers -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;L2 Button</font>	
                  <br>&nbsp; Move view to face cue ball, free viewpoint mode -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;R2 Button</font>	
                  <br>&nbsp; Move view above table -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Select Button</font>					  
                  <br>&nbsp; Menu -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Start Button</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">FREE VIEWPOINT MODE CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Zoom in or out -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad Up or Down</font>			  
                  <br>&nbsp; Rotate camera left or right -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad Left or Right</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Move camera up or down -
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;L1 or R1 Button</font><br><br>	
				  &nbsp;</td>
	 </tr>
	</table>
